Currently, CPU History does everything that I desire: full multicore support, graphing in the Dock icon, dynamic bar sizes and colors, and a fine-grained update interval.\
\
Unfortunately, I now work for Apple, and I'm unsure of the future of this program, including any future updates. There's a lot that would be neat to add, but I haven't heard yet on whether or not I can continue development on this program. If you'd like to pick up the project or fork it, my contact information is further down.\
